    "description": "《教堂模拟器》 是一款第一人称模拟游戏，涵盖了教堂牧师的所有职责，既充满宗教氛围，又具有娱乐性。<br><br>定制您的教堂外观，使其既时尚又吸引人。创建最合适的教堂设计，以吸引更多人前来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/aee71428ef10c4465e607bd2ca610ee4.poster.avif?t=1754989741\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/aee71428ef10c4465e607bd2ca610ee4.webm?t=1754989741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/aee71428ef10c4465e607bd2ca610ee4.mp4?t=1754989741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>从商店购买家具、画作、雕像和座椅，为您的教堂进行室内设计。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/854bf1ac35a235e7939ec054b06a5686.poster.avif?t=1754989741\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/854bf1ac35a235e7939ec054b06a5686.webm?t=1754989741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/854bf1ac35a235e7939ec054b06a5686.mp4?t=1754989741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>将带到教堂的婴儿浸入圣水中进行洗礼。务必正确地进行洗礼操作，否则您可能会将婴儿溺死！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/aa99cff529189b896f4c45e9ad3991aa.poster.avif?t=1754989741\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/aa99cff529189b896f4c45e9ad3991aa.webm?t=1754989741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/aa99cff529189b896f4c45e9ad3991aa.mp4?t=1754989741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>为教堂的货架填满产品并进行排列，以收集捐款。通过销售圣经、蜡烛和纪念品等物品来管理教堂的经济。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/4355d1e8c536272b957b9f03a8435da0.poster.avif?t=1754989741\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/4355d1e8c536272b957b9f03a8435da0.webm?t=1754989741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/4355d1e8c536272b957b9f03a8435da0.mp4?t=1754989741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>用十字架祝福前来教堂的人们，引导他们信仰。证明您是一名真正的牧师。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/4c9aefa7de7f384730ad715c503bdd88.poster.avif?t=1754989741\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/4c9aefa7de7f384730ad715c503bdd88.webm?t=1754989741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/4c9aefa7de7f384730ad715c503bdd88.mp4?t=1754989741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>使用探测器发现并驱散教堂及墓地周围的恶灵。不要让恶灵诅咒您的教堂。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/828df43ef259f862a55f06efc990a3e7.poster.avif?t=1754989741\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/828df43ef259f862a55f06efc990a3e7.webm?t=1754989741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112500/extras/828df43ef259f862a55f06efc990a3e7.mp4?t=1754989741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在**《教堂模拟器》中，通过做出正确的决策来尽力管理好您的教堂。您必须通过收集人们的捐款来维持教堂的经济。此外，您还可以组织婚礼、葬礼、仪式等集体活动。吸引更多的人来到教堂，并扩大您的教堂！此外，还可以喂养流浪动物，解决村里的问题，拜访商人，进行布道，模拟一位真正的牧师的生活。在既宗教和平又幽默有趣的《教堂模拟器》**游戏中，您能否成功管理您的教堂？",
